          <li><strong>HRA exemption:</strong> Based on rent paid — significant for metro employees</li>
          <li><strong>Section 24(b):</strong> Home loan interest up to ₹2,00,000</li>
          <li><strong>Section 80CCD(1B):</strong> Additional ₹50,000 for NPS</li>
          <li><strong>Section 87A rebate:</strong> Income up to ₹5 lakh = zero tax</li>
        </ul>
